2.06 (05-01-2003)
/usr/sbin/cmoduser -n username --set-aliases=""
Adds an alias of "1" (1@domainname.com)

This now sets it to empty.  
(reported by Jared Herbohn of 90blue.com)

2.07 (09-29-2003)
/usr/sbin/cmoduser -n test --forwardOff="" does not work.
